txt.en: A powerful and stealthy morvul stalks the Circle of Madness.
Stalker Thimmoth has fallen by your hand, further protecting the Star-gazers' Spire from the eyes of your enemies.
Stalker Thimmoth can be found scouting the Circle of Madness.\n\nYou should defeat Stalker Thimmoth
You have found a powerful morvul scouting the Circle of Madness. Stalker Thimmoth should be defeated before he discovers the Ranger encampment in the Stargazers' Spire.
